What you need to know:

Djokovic captured a ninth Australian Open last month to take his career Slam tally to 18.Djokovic has also taken Federer's record for weeks at number one with the Serb moving to 311 weeks in total on Monday.Federer has insisted his recovery from knee surgery was "completely under control" ahead of his return to competitive tennis.Federer is an eight-time Wimbledon winner.